net.jbouchard.bool
Class BooleanOperator

java.lang.Object
  net.jbouchard.bool.BooleanOperator

public abstract class BooleanOperator
extends Object

An operator in a boolean expression with precedence and arity. Contains static utility methods to work with operators.

Version:
0.1 Beta
Author:

OPERATORS

arity

private final int arity
The arity of this operator. Arity is the number of operands that an operator takes as arguments

precedence

private final int precedence
The precedence of this operator among other operators. Higher precedence operators are evaluated after lower precedence operators.
